params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"DRAW_CD\\" as \\"DRAW_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"SPEC\\" as \\"SPEC\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" as \\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" as \\"STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"LOT_CTRL_FLG\\") AS \\"LOT_CTRL_FLG\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\"), 'TM9') as \\"ITEM_STOCK_ONHAN_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"DEFECT_QTY\\"), 'TM9') as \\"ITEM_STOCK_DEFECT_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"PRVS_DAYEND_STOCK_QTY\\"), 'TM9') as \\"ITEM_STOCK_DAYEND_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"PRVS_MONTHEND_STOCK_QTY\\"), 'TM9') as \\"ITEM_STOCK_MONTHEND_QTY\\" " +"from " +" T_ITEM_STOCK " +"where " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +"group by " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\""

"select " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\"), 'TM9') as \\"JOB_STOCK_ONHAN_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PRVS_DAYEND_STOCK_QTY\\"), 'TM9') as \\"JOB_STOCK_DAYEND_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PRVS_MONTHEND_STOCK_QTY\\"), 'TM9') as \\"JOB_STOCK_MONTHEND_QTY\\" " +"from " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK " +"where " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +"group by " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\""

"select " +" M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" as \\"MRP_FLG\\", " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\"), 'TM9') as \\"ITEM_STOCK_MRP_QTY\\" " +"from " +" M_WH, " +" T_ITEM_STOCK " +"where " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD " +" and T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +"group by " +" M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\", " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\""

"select " +" M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" as \\"MRP_FLG\\", " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\"), 'TM9') as \\"JOB_STOCK_MRP_QTY\\" " +"from " +" M_WH, " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK " +"where " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +"group by " +" M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\", " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\""

"select " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\",'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"DEFECT_QTY\\",'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"DEFECT_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"PRVS_DAYEND_STOCK_QTY\\",'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"PRVS_DAYEND_STOCK_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"PRVS_MONTHEND_STOCK_QTY\\",'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"PRVS_MONTHEND_STOCK_QTY\\", " +" M_PLANT.\\"PLANT_NAME\\" as \\"PLANT_NAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" as \\"MRP_FLG\\" " +"from " +" T_ITEM_STOCK, " +" M_PLANT, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.PLANT_CD = M_PLANT.PLANT_CD(+) " +" and T_ITEM_STOCK.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +"order by " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\""

"select " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\",'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PRVS_DAYEND_STOCK_QTY\\",'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"PRVS_DAYEND_STOCK_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PRVS_MONTHEND_STOCK_QTY\\",'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"PRVS_MONTHEND_STOCK_QTY\\", " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" as \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", " +" M_PLANT.\\"PLANT_NAME\\" as \\"PLANT_NAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" as \\"MRP_FLG\\" " +"from " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK, " +" M_PLANT, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.PLANT_CD = M_PLANT.PLANT_CD(+) " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +"order by " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" " +""

"SELECT " +" T_LOT_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_PLANT.\\"PLANT_NAME\\" as \\"PLANT_NAME\\", " +" T_LOT_STOCK.\\"LOT_NO\\" as \\"LOT_NO\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_LOT_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\", 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_LOT_STOCK.\\"ALCD_QTY\\", 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"ALCD_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_LOT_CTRL.\\"BEST_BEFORE_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"BEST_BEFORE_DATE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_LOT_CTRL.\\"PRD_CMPLT_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"PRD_CMPLT_DATE\\" " +"FROM " +" T_ITEM_STOCK, " +" T_LOT_STOCK, " +" M_PLANT, " +" T_LOT_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" T_LOT_STOCK.PLANT_CD = M_PLANT.PLANT_CD(+) " +" AND T_LOT_STOCK.LOT_NO = T_LOT_CTRL.LOT_NO(+) " +" AND T_ITEM_STOCK.ITEM_CD = T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD " +" AND T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD = T_LOT_CTRL.ITEM_CD " +" AND T_ITEM_STOCK.WH_CD = T_LOT_STOCK.WH_CD " +" AND T_LOT_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_LOT_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_LOT_CTRL.\\"DEL_FLG\\" = 0 " +"ORDER BY " +" T_LOT_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" T_LOT_STOCK.\\"LOT_NO\\""

"select " +"count(1) " +"from " +" T_ITEM_STOCK, " +" M_PLANT, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.PLANT_CD = M_PLANT.PLANT_CD(+) " +" and T_ITEM_STOCK.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and ROWNUM<=TO_NUMBER(?)+1"

"select " +" count(1) " +"from " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK, " +" M_PLANT, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.PLANT_CD = M_PLANT.PLANT_CD(+) " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"
